tag.name: Work for a start up
tag.description: Being a budding entrepreneur with a brand-new startup is an exciting experience, especially if you are in Germany. The country has one of the most vibrating startup boosters in Europe, with a reputation known for fostering innovation and talent all across the continent. Here you may find some of the major German Startup Ecosystem players everyone should know.

tag.name: Soon to be unicorn
tag.description: Know the feeling of something great about to happen? Well, these start-ups dont only know but are living it. Heres the list of venture-backed companies that have crossed or are soon crossing the $1 billion valuation threshold.

tag.name: Big & Confident
tag.description: These are the true powerhouses in their industry. They know what they are doing and have the numbers to prove it. If you are seeking to start your corporate success story, look no further.

tag.name: Discover Fin-tech
tag.description: The future of finance at its finest - here are the companies working their magic on improving the delivery and use of financial services through technological innovation.

tag.name: TOA19
tag.description: TOA, Europes Leading Technology Festival, is once again showing us the future of tech, work, and life by bringing together the brightest Talents and coolest employers. Were excited to introduce you companies that are ready to meet and greet on the spot during the event.

tag.name: Coolest office
tag.description: What is another element that will make you more productive? Your surroundings. Lots of space for great ideas or a cozy corner with beanbags to unwind. These companies have put the effort in to make their team feel at their best when in the office.

tag.name: Socially and Ecologically Responsible
tag.description: These are the companies that want to give back. On top of aiming to build a successful business they also focus on minimizing harmful effects and being a force for good in society. Change starts from within.
